   Hladun, Kristen R.; Trumble, John T., Univ Calif Riverside, Dept Entomol, Riverside, CA 92521 USA.
   Parker, David R., Univ Calif Riverside, Dept Environm Sci, Riverside, CA 92521 USA.},
